Project Dependencies:

Nodejs - www.nodejs.org
    Note: please install version 6
Express - www.expressjs.com
Leaflet - www.leafletjs.com

===============================================================================

Configuring the environment:

Run the following command to pull the required dependencies:
$ npm install

===============================================================================

Operating the application:

To start the site, run the following from the project root:
$ npm start

To view the map, visit the following URL:
$ localhost:3000/map

